     4| * Owner spec (2026-07-05):
     5| *   Never answer deployment questions with conversational text.
     6| *   Every deployment request must return exactly one of:
     7| *     STATE: READY
     8| *     STATE: RUNNING
     9| *     STATE: BLOCKED
    10| *     STATE: VERIFIED
    11| *
    12| *   If BLOCKED:  return only the exact blocker.
    13| *   If VERIFIED: return GitHub SHA, Render Deploy ID, Health endpoint,
    14| *                Version endpoint, Timestamp, Evidence ledger.
    15| *
    16| *   Never fabricate production evidence.
    17| *   Never claim deployment without verification.
    18| *
    19| * This module is the single source of truth for the strict deployment state
    20| * envelope. It is pure (no I/O) so it is fully unit-testable. All deployment
    21| * handlers (chat brain slash-commands, natural-language deploy intents, the
    22| * public_deploy canned answer, the developer-deploy-control route) MUST format
    23| * their final answer through this module so the owner always receives the same
